PrecisConfirmation of a SPECIFIC AGREEMENT between THE CHIPPEWAS OF SARNIA FIRST NATION AND BAND OF INDIANS, the federal Crown and the Province of Ontario, whereby the Province's fifty percent share of the revenues from the natural gas reserves on Sarnia Indian Reserve No. 45 can be released to the Band.
